//About activity resources
This program intended to calculate atmosphere parameters on altitude from 0 to 85 kilometers above the Earth surface. Also it has possibility to evaluate full parameters of inlet flow during the flight with given altitude and Mach number.\n\n Program: Batura Stas\n Science core: Sidorov Rodion\n
